WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:05.000
narrator: the same join flow on macOS — Homebrew tailscale CLI.

00:00:05.000 --> 00:00:15.000
narrator: brew install tailscale ships the daemon and the CLI binary.

00:00:15.000 --> 00:00:25.000
narrator: launch the daemon as a launchd service on first run.

00:00:25.000 --> 00:00:35.000
narrator: tailscale up points at the operator URL with the preauth key.

00:00:35.000 --> 00:00:45.000
narrator: macOS prompts once for a Network Extension permission grant.

00:00:45.000 --> 00:00:55.000
narrator: the system tray shows the issued 100.64.x.x address.

00:00:55.000 --> 00:01:05.000
narrator: peer enumeration matches the linux flow — same wire protocol.

00:01:05.000 --> 00:01:15.000
narrator: ping to a peer confirms direct WireGuard, no DERP fallback.

00:01:15.000 --> 00:01:25.000
narrator: the macOS host is now joined to the same tailnet.
